org.epics.pvData.misc
Interface Timer.TimerNode

Enclosing interface:
Timer
public static interface Timer.TimerNode

An interface implemented by TimerFactory. Code that wants to insert an element in a Timer must allocate a TimerNode. A TimerNode can only appear in only one Timer at a time and at most once in a particular timer.

Method Summary
 void cancel()
          Cancel the current request.
 

Method Detail

cancel

void cancel()
Cancel the current request. The TimerNode can be reused by calling a schedule method.
